      "text": "Step 2: Wait for Port M to be Ready\n\nRegister: SYSCTL_PRGPIO\n\nAddress: 0x400FEA08\n\nAction: Poll bit 11 until it equals 1",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "umHHaNTVGTOHLqRHdkqCh",
      "originalText": "Step 2: Wait for Port M to be Ready\n\nRegister: SYSCTL_PRGPIO\n\nAddress: 0x400FEA08\n\nAction: Poll bit 11 until it equals 1",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
